 in AHRI 210/240-2024 and AHRI 1600-2024. (
Id.
) Finally, Rheem pointed to a typographical error in sections I4.3.1.4 of AHRI 210/240-2024 and AHRI 1600-2024, and it made suggestions for correcting it.
